    • Method Detail

      • defaultAssignment

        private void defaultAssignment()
        This method assigns the minimum and maximum values by default. The values on of the first line or first time frame being recorded will automatically be the maximum value and also will be the minimum value. This way, the calculation methods can work correctly.
